Usage: specifyLockupElement [-help] [-in <ftname>] [-out <ftname>]
                            {-cell <leafCellName> | -inst <instName>}

-help                    # Prints out the command usage
-cell <leafCellName>     # Specify the cell to be lockup element.
                         # (string, required)
-in <ftname>             # Specify the name of scan input. (string, optional)
-inst <instName>         # Specify the instance to be lockup element.
                         # (string, required)
-out <ftname>            # Specify the name of scan output. (string, optional)